## CCSelectorState.significantDigits property

> This API is provided as an alpha preview for developers and may change based on feedback that we receive. Do not use this API in a production environment.
> 

The digits of the phone number that are significant in terms of the country code. Contains only the digits without visual separator characters or the plus sign.

**Signature:**

```typescript
significantDigits: string;
```
